Class Enquiry

Object
Enquiry
public class Enquiry extends Object
Represents an enquiry submitted by an applicant regarding a specific BTO project. Contains the enquiry message, a reply (if any), and the timestamp of creation.

    • Enquiry

      public Enquiry(Applicant applicant, BTOProject project, String message)
      Constructs an Enquiry object with the specified applicant, project, and message. Initializes the timestamp to the current time and marks the enquiry as not replied.
      Parameters:
      applicant - The applicant who submitted the enquiry
      project - The BTO project related to the enquiry
      message - The message content of the enquiry
